[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     34[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 3: Shift Detection Matches on `suggested_label` Which Is Non-Deterministic Across Runs
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     35[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
